Name: XNNPACK
Short Name: xnnpack
URL: https://github.com/google/xnnpack
Version: 3363df1c21d8b3cc2bb8d317959e89bcdf3f4f38
Date: 2024-06-27
License: BSD
License File: src/LICENSE
Security Critical: Yes
Shipped: yes

Description:
XNNPACK is a highly optimized library of floating-point neural network inference
operators for ARM, WebAssembly, and x86 platforms. This library supports
//third_party/tflite.

Note that the BUILD.gn file is generated by `generate_build_gn.py` in this
directory.

The build_identifier.c file in this directory is generated by `bazel build
generate_build_identifier` and file will be created in `bazel-bin/src/`.
